value.name: Epic - An Around the World Journey through Christian History
value.original_name: Epic - An Around the World Journey through Christian History
value.overview: Through thirty-three objects, Tim Challies explores the history of what God is accomplishing in this world, whether through princes or peasants, triumph or trial. Each object offers a tangible link between the present and the past, between Christians of the twenty-first century and those who lived and died centuries past. Join us on the journey of a lifetime!
